description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Edited in the UK by Rachel Shelley.


What are you watching at the moment? And does it get pet approval?

With so much time at home, so many hours on the couch, and so many platforms to choose from,

it's good to know a professional TV watcher who takes pride in her work.


Mo with the Direwolves. The highlight of Kate's personal quarantine.



Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram ThePantsPod

Email us: pantspodcast@yahoo.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx
